{"id":564,"date":"2020-10-23T16:59:34","date_gmt":"2020-10-23T14:59:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/?p=564"},"modified":"2020-10-23T16:59:36","modified_gmt":"2020-10-23T14:59:36","slug":"the-2nd-triple-consortium-meeting-virtual-intense-dynamic","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/2020\/10\/the-2nd-triple-consortium-meeting-virtual-intense-dynamic\/","title":{"rendered":"The 2nd TRIPLE Consortium Meeting: Virtual, Intense, Dynamic"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"modal-ready\">\n<p>Two intense and dynamic half days of virtual meetings have come to a close. From the 19 consortium partners, 57 participants gathered to present ongoing work and next steps. Challenges and how to meet these were also addressed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-medium is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Consortium-Meeting2b-Kopie-300x270.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-575\" width=\"404\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Consortium-Meeting2b-Kopie-300x270.png 300w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Consortium-Meeting2b-Kopie-1024x922.png 1024w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Consortium-Meeting2b-Kopie-768x692.png 768w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Consortium-Meeting2b-Kopie.png 1519w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 404px) 100vw, 404px\" \/><figcaption>Screenshot of the Zoom meeting room on day 1 of the Consortium Meeting<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>The TRIPLE project coordinator, <a href=\"https:\/\/operas.hypotheses.org\/4147\">Suzanne Dumouchel<\/a>, opened the Consortium Meeting by welcoming all participants. The rest of the first day was then dedicated to updates from the eight <a href=\"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/?page_id=35\">work packages<\/a>. The highlight was definitely the videos of the offices and staff from partners in work package 5!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-medium is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Consortium-Meeting3b-Kopie-300x263.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-574\" width=\"409\" height=\"359\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Consortium-Meeting3b-Kopie-300x263.png 300w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Consortium-Meeting3b-Kopie-1024x899.png 1024w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Consortium-Meeting3b-Kopie-768x674.png 768w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Consortium-Meeting3b-Kopie-1536x1348.png 1536w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Consortium-Meeting3b-Kopie.png 1559w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 409px) 100vw, 409px\" \/><figcaption>Two parallel sessions on day 2: The Data Management Plan and relationships between TRIPLE and other projects<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>The agenda of the second day included the presentation of the results of a survey among the consortium members and two breakout sessions. One group discussed the TRIPLE Data Management Plan while the other group explored synergies between TRIPLE and other projects such as <a href=\"https:\/\/sshopencloud.eu\/\">Social Sciences &amp; Humanities Open Cloud (SSHOC)<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Two intense and dynamic half days of virtual meetings have come to a close. From the 19 consortium partners, 57 participants gathered to present ongoing work and next steps. Challenges and how to meet these were also addressed. The TRIPLE<\/p>\n","protecte